\"from\": 450, \"to\": 473}, {\"ngram\": \"the quarter-finals\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 501}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's doubles\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the drama of Sunday's five-match-point-saving comeback to defeat Japanese duoTaro Danieland Kei Nishikori, it appeared this would be slightly less nail-biting when they brought up two match points in the second-set tie-break against Belgian duo Sander Gille and Joran Vliegen.\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 808, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 624, \"end\": 637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kei_Nishikori\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kei Nishikori\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kei_Nishikori\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kei_Nishikori\"}, {\"begin\": 765, \"end\": 772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999836923136208, \"rank\": 1.4672021107665564e-05, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 794, \"end\": 807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joran_Vliegen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Joran Vliegen\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joran_Vliegen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joran_Vliegen\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the drama\", \"from\": 532, \"to\": 541}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday's five-match-point-saving comeback\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 586}, {\"ngram\": \"two match points\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 728}, {\"ngram\": \"the second-set tie-break\", \"from\": 732, \"to\": 756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But instead, Murray and Evans were taken to another match tie-break by last year's French Open finalists and had to save two more match points before claiming a 6-3 6-7 (8) (11/9) victory and a place in the last eight.\", \"from\": 810, \"to\": 1028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 823, \"end\": 829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.685410640069437e-52, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 834, \"end\": 839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999879914868, \"rank\": 1.2008606071074067e-08, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another match tie-break\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 877}, {\"ngram\": \"last year's French Open finalists\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 914}, {\"ngram\": \"two more match points\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 952}, {\"ngram\": \"a 6-3 6-7 (8) (11/9) victory\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 997}, {\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1009}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray and Evans again bounced around the court with joy after the latter put away the decisive volley before the moment caught up with the Scot and he sat on his chair with head in hands.\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1030, \"end\": 1036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.685410640069437e-52, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1041, \"end\": 1046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999879914868, \"rank\": 1.2008606071074067e-08, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1077}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1086}, {\"ngram\": \"the latter\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1103}, {\"ngram\": \"the decisive volley\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1132}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 1140, \"to\": 1150}, {\"ngram\": \"the Scot\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1174}, {\"ngram\": \"his chair\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1198}, {\"ngram\": \"head\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1208}, {\"ngram\": \"hands\", \"from\": 1212, \"to\": 1217}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Court Suzanne Lenglen was again less than half empty when Murray and Evans walked out, with many fans having left after watching Rafael Nadal and Carlos Alcaraz reach the quarter-finals.\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1406, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1220, \"end\": 1241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Court Suzanne Lenglen\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_Roland_Garros\"}, {\"begin\": 1278, \"end\": 1284, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.685410640069437e-52, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1289, \"end\": 1294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999879914868, \"rank\": 1.2008606071074067e-08, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}, {\"begin\": 1349, \"end\": 1361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rafael Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}, {\"begin\": 1366, \"end\": 1380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many fans\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1321}, {\"ngram\": \"the quarter-finals\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1405}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It seemed that those who were left, though, nearly all waved British flags as they sought to create a fitting atmosphere.\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1529, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1469, \"end\": 1476, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9917098807641022, \"rank\": 0.007036943923062539, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nearly all\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1462}, {\"ngram\": \"a fitting atmosphere\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1528}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The British pair had spoken of the need to start much better than in their great escape on Sunday and they were as good as their word, both men hitting return winners in Vliegen's opening service game before an Evans lob landed right in the corner to give them an immediate break.\", \"from\": 1531, \"to\": 1811, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1535, \"end\": 1542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9917098807641022, \"rank\": 0.007036943923062539, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}, {\"begin\": 1742, \"end\": 1747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999879914868, \"rank\": 1.2008606071074067e-08, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the need\", \"from\": 1562, \"to\": 1570}, {\"ngram\": \"their great escape\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1618}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1628}, {\"ngram\": \"their word\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1664}, {\"ngram\": \"both men\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1674}, {\"ngram\": \"return winners\", \"from\": 1683, \"to\": 1697}, {\"ngram\": \"Vliegen's opening service game\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"the corner\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1778}, {\"ngram\": \"an immediate break\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1810}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Murray in particular was so much sharper than he had been in the first round, hitting the ball crisply off the ground and dominating at the net, while Evans was hugely fired up throughout.\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 2001, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1964, \"end\": 1969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999879914868, \"rank\": 1.2008606071074067e-08, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Murray\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1819}, {\"ngram\": \"the first round\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1889}, {\"ngram\": \"the ball\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1907}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1930}, {\"ngram\": \"the net\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1956}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was then Murray's turn to show off his famous lobbing skills as he made it 3-0, and the only real wobble of the opening set occurred with Evans serving at 5-3.\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2015, \"end\": 2021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.685410640069437e-52, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 2144, \"end\": 2149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999879914868, \"rank\": 1.2008606071074067e-08, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his famous lobbing skills\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2066}, {\"ngram\": \"the only real wobble\", \"from\": 2090, \"to\": 2110}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening set\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2129}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was given a time violation for taking too long before serving and then threw his racket to the clay after Vliegen's return hit the tape and landed in to give the Belgians break point, but Evans saved it and eventually held.\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2393, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2358, \"end\": 2363, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999879914868, \"rank\": 1.2008606071074067e-08, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a time violation\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2196}, {\"ngram\": \"his racket\", \"from\": 2247, \"to\": 2257}, {\"ngram\": \"the clay\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2269}, {\"ngram\": \"Vliegen's return\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2292}, {\"ngram\": \"the tape\", \"from\": 2297, \"to\": 2305}, {\"ngram\": \"the Belgians\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2340}, {\"ngram\": \"break point\", \"from\": 2341, \"to\": 2352}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Serve dominated in the second set until Murray and Evans pressed Vliegen at 4-4, the Scot showing an extended fist pump to the crowd and Evans twice forcing break points but the Belgians responded well on serve both times.\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2617, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2435, \"end\": 2441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.685410640069437e-52, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 2446, \"end\": 2451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999879914868, \"rank\": 1.2008606071074067e-08, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}, {\"begin\": 2532, \"end\": 2537, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999879914868, \"rank\": 1.2008606071074067e-08, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Serve\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2400}, {\"ngram\": \"the second set\", \"from\": 2414, \"to\": 2428}, {\"ngram\": \"Vliegen\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2467}, {\"ngram\": \"the Scot\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2484}, {\"ngram\": \"an extended fist pump\", \"from\": 2493, \"to\": 2514}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowd\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2527}, {\"ngram\": \"break points\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2564}, {\"ngram\": \"the Belgians\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It came down to a tie-break, and Murray and Evans did themselves no favours with an early double fault each.\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2727, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2652, \"end\": 2658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.685410640069437e-52, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 2663, \"end\": 2668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9999999879914868, \"rank\": 1.2008606071074067e-08, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tie-break\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2646}, {\"ngram\": \"no favours\", \"from\": 2684, \"to\": 2694}, {\"ngram\": \"an early double fault\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They still forced two match points but the Belgians saved them both and another Evans double fault sent the contest to a decider.\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2857, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two match points\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2762}, {\"ngram\": \"the Belgians\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2779}, {\"ngram\": \"double fault\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 2826}, {\"ngram\": \"the contest\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2843}, {\"ngram\": \"a decider\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2856}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The momentum swung from one pair to the other until Gille and Vliegen created two match points at 9-7 but Murray and Evans again simply refused to be beaten.\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 3016, \"entit